### 1. 대화방 생성 (POST /api/conversations)
POST http://localhost:8081/api/conversations?userId=1&title=통일된주소테스트
Content-Type: application/json

### 2. 메시지 전송 (POST /api/conversations/{id}/messages)
# 위에서 나온 ID가 1이라고 가정
POST http://localhost:8081/api/conversations/5/messages
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "content": "혹시 JAVA에 대해서 설명해줄래?"
}

### 3. 대화방 목록 조회 (GET /api/conversations)
GET http://localhost:8081/api/conversations

### 4.대화방 상세 조회 (GET /api/conversations/{id})
GET http://localhost:8081/api/conversations/5

### 5.대화방 메시지 내역 조회 (GET /api/conversations/{id}/messages)
GET http://localhost:8081/api/conversations/5/messages

### 6.대화방 삭제 (DELETE /api/conversations/{id})
DELETE http://localhost:8081/api/conversations/5